t professionals with key leaders from both firms signing contracts over  unique investment offerings across  different investmentstrategies a materially larger investment platform ranging from opportunistic coinvestments with longer duration lockedup capital tailrisk hedging strategies and bespoked customized investment solutions a more rapid evolution of innovative alternative products and lines of business including direct hedge funds and private debt offerings increased sources of proprietary investment opportunities ability to broaden the organizations innovative existing managed account platform joseph a sullivan chairman and ceo of legg mason said the combined entrustpermal brings together two leading names in the alternative space creating a significant potential growth engine for legg mason  the team at entrust has a proven track record for driving significant organic growth through product innovation with over  growth annually since the financial crisis  we see meaningful opportunities to combine this innovation with permals blue chip client base product offering and global footprint gregg s hymowitz managing partner of entrust said the combination of entrust and permal creates a powerful organization in the hedge fund universe  entrustpermals scale resources and global investment talent will be able to deliver market differentiated proprietary investments to our over  combined institutional accounts and significant number of highnet worth investors  the complementary nature of our investment strategies geographies and global investorpartner base dramatically springboards us over our competition   the entrust and permal teams are eager to start delivering for our loyal investor base omar kodmani permal group chief executive officer said the future of our industry is about offering alternative investment solutions on multiple fronts  to achieve this you need scale and talent and entrustpermal combines both  we currently have one of the best resourced investment teams in the industry and which when paired with entrust offers more to our clients and strengthens our business the combination is expected to close in mid  the transaction is expected to be modestly accretive to legg masons earnings in the first year after giving effect to estimated cost savings achieved that year and excluding restructuring and transition charges   legg mason expects entrustpermal to achieve cost savings of approximately  million per year  in connection with the combination of the businesses legg mason expects to incur restructuring and transition costs of approximately  million beginning in the companys th fiscal quarter of  and continuing throughout fiscal year   morgan stanley  co llc has acted as financial advisor to legg mason in connection with this transaction goldman sachs acted as the financial advisor to entrust with respect to the transaction about entrust  entrust capital is a leading alternative asset management firm with approximately  billion in total assets as of december   entrust manages assets for over  institutional accounts and has over  billion in customized strategic partnerships with institutional investors including over  billion in longer duration opportunistic capital  entrust is headquartered in new york city about legg mason   legg mason is a global asset management firm with  billion in assets under management as of december   the company provides active asset management in many major investment centers throughout the world legg mason is headquartered in baltimore maryland and its common stock is listed on the new york stock exchange symbol lm  excludes permal capital management aum of approximately  billion which will be separated from entrustpermal   total assets include aum assets under advisory and unfunded contractually committed assets to view the original version on pr newswire visithttpwwwprnewswirecomnewsreleasesleggmasonannouncescombinationofentrustcapitalandpermalgrouphtml source legg mason inc related