unds products for international investors permal founded in  operates one of the oldest fund of hedge funds and manages approximately  billion in assets clients include sovereign wealth funds pension funds endowments foundations insurance companies family offices private banks and highnetworth individuals its ceo is omar kodmani and its chairman is isaac r souede permal is headquartered in london with offices in new york boston singapore paris nassau dubai hong kong and beijing contents  history  investment funds  references  external links historyedit in  permal was acquired by legg mason in an  million transaction and operates as a subsidiary of that company in  permal acquired fauchier partners a leading european based manager of funds of hedge funds from bnp paribas investment partners in  is was announced that the permal group subsidiary would merge with entrust capital to increase assets investment fundsedit permal offers a range of multimanager multistrategy funds as well as single manager funds and customized separate accounts the firms flagship product permal investment holding was launched in  and is a global multistrategy fund of hedge funds managed by robert kaplan the fund aims to capture two thirds of the upside during a bull market and seeks to limit its downside to one third of a comparable index during the bear market permal also operates as a private equity fund of funds and secondary investment firm through its subsidiary permal capital management in  legg mason announced it would merge its permal group subsidiary with entrust capital to increase assets managed by its hedge fundsoffunds business to  billion referencesedit  a b introduction – the permal group permalcom   biographies permalcom   legg mason closes on m deal baltimore daily record november    legg mason inc  march  legg mason and permal complete acquisition of fauchier partners prnewswirecom   kozlowski rob  university of maine sticks with entrustpermal following merger pensions  inve